9. **No Clear Path Specification**: If the file doesn't specify parent-child relationships clearly, deducing the path to a particular node can be problematic.

10. **Resource Limitations**: Depending on the size and complexity of the tree, system resource limitations (memory, CPU) could impact the ability to parse and process the file.
